name: Adam Lippes Set of 4 Roseraie Floral Dinner Plates - Multi
description: Inspired by antique famille rose porcelain, fashionable in Europe during the Late Baroque period, our Roseraie china range features a menagerie of colorful flora and fauna. Roses in all shades of pink bloom alongside fruit trees bearing persimmon, lychees and papaya, welcoming birds of paradise and butterflies into the garden. Elevate everyday dining with these beautiful floral patterned dinner plates, made from fine bone china.
